{"tid":1320152,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今朝喺柴灣飲茶，撚到個廢老冇嘢好講","createTime":"2019-07-15T10:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T02:37:10.000Z","uid":143499,"like":135,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b85d20887ee39e4283fee3d00a10e599eb7a471e","tid":1320152,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:18:01.000Z","msg":"廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :而家呢代淨係識出嚟投訴呢樣投訴嗰樣， 少少唔滿意政府就咁多嘢搞，唔捱得，冇撚用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :阿叔你以前好巴閉嘅咩?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 當年我大陸游水落嚟遊咗三日三夜，一日打三份工，仲要同英國佬打，靚仔你打個工未呀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 我直接打共產黨喎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後個廢老就收咗皮，feel到附近推點心嘅阿姐用好仰慕嘅眼神望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c53423c5563f65a20a617f63d5d9f5438406363","tid":1320152,"uid":182792,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:23:42.000Z","msg":"咁涯得中共游水落黎把撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42fa3b49a82a6cce813956433916f5f833e439bf","tid":1320152,"uid":143499,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8c53423c5563f65a20a617f63d5d9f5438406363","tid":1320152,"uid":182792,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:23:42.000Z","msg":"咁涯得中共游水落黎把撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:24:48.000Z","msg":"共產黨好偉大㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676db4b27df0a5b049066433ee02c07c83c3d22c","tid":1320152,"uid":37586,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:26:58.000Z","msg":"同阿